        "item_ship_packages": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How do you ship your packages?",
            "content": "<p>Here at Grasscity, we understand our customers' concerns about privacy and discretion. Every product we ship is sent in plain cardboard boxes, with nothing to mark glass pipes or smokeware. Our shipping labels do not say Grasscity, and we do everything we can to ensure our packages are discreet.</p><p>Our packages are shipped to you in standard shipping boxes (either a plain brown box or a USPS Priority Mail box). Nowhere on the outside of your package will you see the word \"Grasscity\".</p><p>However, \"Grasscity\" will appear on your credit card statement. We cannot change this, and we apologize in advance for any inconvenience this may cause.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": true,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_ship_cost": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How much does shipping cost?",
            "content": "<p>We offer free domestic shipping within the United States on orders over $50. For international orders, we currently only ship to Canada, with a flat shipping rate of $14.95 for all orders.</p><p><strong>Our Shipping Team and Shipping Speeds</strong></p><p>Please note that shipping speed does not include order processing time. Orders typically require 2-3 business days for processing, including pulling and packaging your items. Our shipping team works hard to dispatch orders as quickly as possible, but during peak seasons and promotional events, processing times may increase.</p><p>Shipping times do not guarantee the exact package arrival date and may be affected by unforeseen circumstances, such as weather conditions or carrier delays.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_ship_address_change": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Can I change my shipping address after placing an order?",
            "content": "<p>Once an order has been placed, we process it quickly to ensure fast delivery. This means we cannot guarantee changes to the shipping address after the order is submitted. If you notice an error immediately after ordering, please contact our customer support team on live chat or email us at support@grasscity.com. We will do our best to help before the order ships.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        }
      },
