        "item_track_package": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How do I track my package?",
            "content": "<p>Tracking information will be sent to you once your order has been scanned and packed up. Tracking emails are typically sent out 1-2 days after your order has been placed.</p><p>Once it ships, you will continue to receive periodic shipping updates until arrival. If you entered a phone number at checkout, our system will send text message alerts when your package is out for delivery.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_where_order": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Where is my order?",
            "content": "<p>Trying to find your package? You can use the tracking link from your shipping email to track your order.</p><p>If you are still having difficulty tracking your order, or if you have additional questions, please contact our customer service for further details.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_signature_required": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Is a signature required for my order?",
            "content": "<p>Grasscity may require a signature for certain orders at our discretion to ensure security. This helps prevent fraud, underage purchases, and other unauthorized activity.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_price_matching": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Does Grasscity offer price matching?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. We offer a Price Match Guarantee with a 5% price beat on eligible items. If you find an identical product from the same brand at a lower price from our online competitors, we are happy to match or beat the listed price. This policy excludes wholesalers and auction sites. Please contact us to request a price match.</p><p>*Terms and conditions apply.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_order_confirmation_email": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What should I do if I did not receive my order confirmation email?",
            "content": "<p>If you have not received your order confirmation, first check your spam or junk folder. If it is not there, please ensure you entered the correct email address at checkout.</p><p>You can also contact our customer support team on live chat or email us at support@grasscity.com with your order details, and we will confirm your order and provide any necessary updates.</p>",
