        "item_returns_policy": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Do you accept returns?",
            "content": "<p>We accept returns on all unused products. If the product has been used, even once, we cannot accept a return - no exceptions. Items must be reported for return within 48 hours of delivery. All returns are subject to a restocking fee.</p><p>If you want to return an item, first email us with pictures of the item so we can verify it is not broken and has not been used. Please note that return shipping cost will be deducted from your refund.</p><p>Returns are accepted only if processed through our customer service team. Packages sent without our return label will not be accepted or refunded.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_cancel_order": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What if I choose to cancel my order?",
            "content": "<p>If the package has already shipped, the order cannot be canceled. If you are unsure about your purchase, please contact us beforehand so we can help you select the best piece for your needs.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_missing_item": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What should I do if an item is missing from my package?",
            "content": "<p>If something is missing from your package, we are really sorry about that. Email us with what is missing from the order, and we will review our order photos and videos for a discrepancy.</p><p>If the photos or video show we made a mistake, we will make it right immediately and send a replacement shipment. Always check your packaging and bubble wrap for missing items, as smaller items can get misplaced during unwrapping.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_exchange_product": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Can I exchange an item for a different product?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, exchanges are available for unused items. Contact customer service within 48 hours of delivery at support@grasscity.com or through live chat. We will coordinate an exchange of equal value and provide a prepaid return label.</p><p>The item must be completely unused, not even one session.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_initiate_return_exchange": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How do I initiate a return or exchange?",
            "content": "<p>To start a return or exchange, contact our customer support team via live chat or email with your order details. They will guide you through the process and provide a return authorization if applicable.</p><p>Only orders reported within 48 hours of delivery are eligible for return.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_return_shipping_cost": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Do I have to pay for return shipping?",
            "content": "<p>For standard returns of not-needed items, you will receive a shipping label, but return shipping cost will be deducted from your refund or store credit.</p><p>If the return is due to a damaged, defective, or incorrect product, we will provide a prepaid shipping label at no cost to you.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_discounted_return": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Can I return a product I bought with a discount?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, discounted items may be returnable if eligible, depending on our terms and conditions and any specific details mentioned in the product description.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
