        "item_help_not_here": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "The answer to my question is not here, what do I do?",
            "content": "<p>If you cannot find the answer to your question, contact us directly. Email us with your name, order number (if applicable), and your question at support@grasscity.com. You can also reach us through the chat widget on our website to connect with a live support agent, available 7 days a week from 9 AM to 9 PM EST.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_glass_safe": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Is Grasscity's glass safe to use?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, all our curated glass pieces are made from body-safe, heat-resistant borosilicate glass (the same material used in lab equipment and kitchenware). It is non-toxic, contains no lead or harmful chemicals, and does not leach or off-gas. Our silicone products use food-grade, BPA-free, phthalate-free platinum-cured silicone. Always inspect glass before use and never use cracked or damaged pieces.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_products_legal": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Are Grasscity products legal?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, all smoking accessories we sell are legal for tobacco use and intended for adult customers ages 21+. Customers are responsible for knowing local laws. We verify age at checkout and may require signature delivery. We reserve the right to cancel orders suspected of violating laws or company policy. We take preventing illicit and underage orders extremely seriously.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "item_sell_to_minors": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Does Grasscity sell to minors?",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely not. We enforce strict 21+ age verification at checkout, reserve the right to require signature on any order for security, and immediately cancel suspected underage orders. Fraud prevention measures are in place throughout our system. For legal guardians ordering for personal use, packages require adult signature to ensure compliance with regulations. No exceptions.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        }
      },
